headline: Regions Wealth Management Names Paige Daniel Head of Highland Associates
summary: BIRMINGHAM, Ala., May 19, 2025--Regions Bank on Monday announced Paige Daniel has been elevated to serve as head of Highland Associates, Inc., a subsidiary of Regions Financial Corp. that serves the investment allocation needs of not-for-profit healthcare entities and mission-based organizations.
